# Index
bind index <Return> select-entry

bind index j next-entry
bind index k previous-entry

bind index J next-new
bind index K previous-new

bind index \Cf next-page
bind index \Cb previous-page
bind index \Cd half-down
bind index \Cu half-up
bind index \Ce next-line
bind index \Cy previous-line

bind index H top-page
bind index M middle-page
bind index L bottom-page

bind index gg first-entry
bind index G last-entry

bind index <Space> toggle-new
bind index <Tab> flag-message

bind index m mail
bind index r reply
bind index R group-reply

bind index \Cr sync-mailbox

